  "detailed_description": "Ancient knowledge is a story in which you will explore the ruins of settlements of the powerful ancient civilization that lived here long time ago, overcoming the traps and puzzles they left.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMain features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Nice low poly graphics and attention to detail<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Magical atmosphere that will allow you to immerse yourself in the culture of ancient India<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Explore ancient palaces and temples, overcoming many traps<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  A large number of different types of puzzles",
  "about_the_game": "Ancient knowledge is a story in which you will explore the ruins of settlements of the powerful ancient civilization that lived here long time ago, overcoming the traps and puzzles they left.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMain features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Nice low poly graphics and attention to detail<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Magical atmosphere that will allow you to immerse yourself in the culture of ancient India<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  Explore ancient palaces and temples, overcoming many traps<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   -  A large number of different types of puzzles",
